    "source": {
      "goCharacterKey": "Venti",
      "note": "Generated from Genshin Optimizer sheets (master) + allStat_gen skillParam. Hit keys match GO target paths; multKey = <hitKey>_mult. Levels: Lv10, except constellation-boosted talents of 4-star characters at Lv13 (C6 assumed). Normal/charged/plunging default to physical unless the sheet overrides the element (infusions are NOT applied). 2026-07: added burst.stormeye (GO burst skillParam index 1, Lv10 = 0.3384) — the periodic Stormeye tick, previously missing from hit_definitions_json. 2026-07-11: added burst.absorb (Amber talent id 3 promote params, Lv10 param2 = 0.3384, officially labeled 'Additional Elemental DMG') — the one-time Elemental Absorption bonus DMG dealt if the Stormeye contacts Hydro/Pyro/Cryo/Electro (once per burst use, per the in-game description). The absorbed element is genuinely team-dependent and this evaluator only supports one fixed element per hit definition, so 'pyro' was chosen to match leaderboard #327 'Venti Hypercarry' (paired with Durin/Nicole, both Pyro). If a future leaderboard needs a different absorbed element, add a sibling hit key (e.g. absorbHydro/absorbCryo/absorbElectro) reusing absorb_mult and point that leaderboard's rotation target at it instead.",
      "assumptions": {
        "constellation": 0,
        "characterLevel": 90,
        "autoTalentLevel": 10,
        "skillTalentLevel": 10,
        "burstTalentLevel": 10
      }
    }
